      <title>Go 模板语法完全指南 —— Hugo 模板开发手册</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/blog/2026/03/go-%E6%A8%A1%E6%9D%BF%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A8%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97-hugo-%E6%A8%A1%E6%9D%BF%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E6%89%8B%E5%86%8C/</link>
